				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Noting that a recent edit by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qwags" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1607757&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529813608" alt="Qwags" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1607757)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qwags" >Qwags</a></span> was reverted, as it incorrectly introduced a url relating to a page in the &quot;deleted:&quot; category.</p> <p>Such pages are considered improperly deleted, and per the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/deletions-guide">Deletion Guidelines</a>, are routinely removed by staff and considered summary deletions. Editors, please refrain from linking to any pages with &quot;deleted:&quot; in the title.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5500353#post-3830614</guid>
				<title>Calling All Authors</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5500353/scp-series-3-tales-edition#post-3830614</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 10 Jun 2018 00:55:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Shaggydredlocks</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1722371</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Holy Moley!!!!</p> <p>A wild &quot;Series 4 Tales Mainlist&quot; WIP has been spotted!!!</p> <table class="wiki-content-table"> <tr> <td>Bag</td> <td>Fight</td> </tr> <tr> <td><a href="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/collab:series-4-mainlist-tales-edition">Here is the list</a></td> <td>Run</td> </tr> </table> <p>If you have a Series 4 SCP that is not on the list (has not been updated in some time) feel free to add them. If they have any derivative works (Tales, Goi-Formats,etc) be sure to list them underneath their respective SCP.</p> <p>The Series 4 Mainlist Tales Edition will be released to the wiki once Series 5 has been opened.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
